  "title": "Telemarketer (Equipment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of generate new leads for the sales team by calling manufacturing contacts to introduce products and services of the company.</li>\n  <li>Identifying and qualifying potential leads for the sales team.</li>\n  <li>Consistently achieving or exceeding sales quotas and performance goals.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min O Level and above</li>\n  <li>Min 1 year of working experience in Cold Calling</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call <strong>+(65)</strong> <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd<br>\nEA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
